==English==

===Noun===
'''dapple'''

# A mottled marking, usually in clusters.
# An [[animal]] with a [[mottled]] or [[spotted]] skin or coat.

===Adjective===
'''dapple'''

# Having a [[mottled]] or [[spotted]] skin or coat, [[dappled]].

